<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-4354] TSocket block on read</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-4354</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When \Thrift\Transport\TSocket::read is called, it will block until receive $len byte(&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/blob/master/lib/php/lib/Thrift/Transport/TSocket.php#L273-L276&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;TSocket.php#L273-L276&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But, sometimes, other call TSocket::read with large length,&lt;br/&gt;
such as &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/blob/39310dad793ca69b4b7217a3b54430e682e5e2a4/lib/php/lib/Thrift/Transport/TBufferedTransport.php#L136-L138&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;TBufferedTransport&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (TStringFuncFactory::create()-&amp;gt;strlen($&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;gt;rBuf_) === 0) {
      $&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;gt;rBuf_ = $&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;gt;transport_-&amp;gt;read($&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;gt;rBufSize_);
    }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;php7.0 + macOS&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
